race.comment: SANCTUARY STORM (8) looked good saluting over this mile journey last time out at Doomben and will have taken a stack of confidence from that victory. Maps perfectly for this from gate four and should give backers a sight. EVELYN MAY (5) was a touch disappointing last time out but the three runs prior were good enough for a race like this. Worth another chance. BOONDOCKS (2) strips fitter third-up from the spell and gets 3kg off with the claim. Top-three credentials on best figures. FARWEST (4) has placed three from three over this trip and looks a must for the exotics players. TECHNA (11) is a last-start winner who draws favourably. Include in calculations.
